<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="compromise-n">compromise <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɒmprəmaɪz/    美 /'kɑːmprəmaɪz/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 妥协；让步；和解：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make a compromise</strong>
作出妥协</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>arrive at / come to / reach a compromise</strong> 
达成妥协</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Most important of all, it is always wise to make decisions by compromise and agreement. 
最重要的是，通过相互妥协、相互协商来作决定总是明智的。</p><footer>2008 江苏</footer></div></div>